00:01:09.950 --> 00:01:12.230
SANJAY BAKSHI: Thank you,
Sarab for inviting me here.

00:01:12.230 --> 00:01:13.355
It's a pleasure to be here.

00:01:13.355 --> 00:01:16.240
It's a wonderful campus and
