competitive advantage.

00:40:55.270 --> 00:40:57.360
They've got better
people, they're tenacious,

00:40:57.360 --> 00:40:59.297
and they're likely
to come out stronger.

00:40:59.297 --> 00:41:00.880
It's an important
distinction that I'm

00:41:00.880 --> 00:41:02.950
trying to make that
the qualitative is

00:41:02.950 --> 00:41:04.660
becoming more important.

00:41:04.660 --> 00:41:06.460
I still think
quantitative features are

00:41:06.460 --> 00:41:08.460
subordinate to the business
model in valuation,

00:41:08.460 --> 00:41:11.200
